title: 1888-89 Old Judge Cabinet N173 Charlie Bennett
author: jcgage0

posts.post_title: 1888-89 Old Judge Cabinet N173 Charlie Bennett
posts.post_content:
Only four of these graded between PSA and SGC.  $1300.  Cashiers check or MO only.  It has a tear on in the upper left hand corner that is held together by tape on the back.  The photo has very good eye appeal.  Very cool card!
